---
title: Quick Chipotle Beef & Black Bean Loaded Wedges with Radish Salsa & Smokey Aioli
description: A cross between nachos and stuffed baked potatoes, these loaded wedges are the ultimate comfort food. Pile them high with
saucy chipotle beef, black beans, radish salsa and smokey aioli, then get cosy and tuck in!
